  <div class="column_holder">
    <h1>
      <img alt="JOBS" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=JOBS" />
    </h1>
    <div class="column_heading">
      <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblTop"><p>GRIN is constantly looking for talented people. All available positions are listed below. Apply via the form or by e-mail.  If you are interested in a position that isn&rsquo;t listed, please send your CV via e-mail to jobs@grin.se.</p></span></div>
    <div class="column_sep">
      <img src="img/jobs/jobs_open_sep.png" alt="Open positions" /></div>
    
    
      <div class="column_content">
        <h1>
          <img alt="Tuesday 29 April 2008" src="/images/headers/pf_small/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Tuesday 29 April 2008" />
        </h1>
        <h2>
          <img alt="IT technician/QA Barcelona" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=IT technician/QA Barcelona" />
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblJobText"><p class="MsoNormal">Work as part time IT-support, and part time as part of the internal QA team, helping with the testing process. <br />
<br />
Although the above will constitute the majority of the job this position is considered &quot;junior&quot; and applicants should be prepared to help out with various tasks around the office as the need arises.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong style=""><span lang="EN-US" style="">Responsibilities<o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>
<ul>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Pinpoint errors in PC computers, replacing the broken parts. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Client support, Windows XP and Vista. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Maintain the bug database. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Data management. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Assist with the testing process of all our projects (bug hunting).</span></li>
    <li><span lang="EN-US" style="">Assist with various tasks around the office. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong style=""><span lang="EN-US" style="">Requirements<o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>
<ul>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Symbol;"><span style=""><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;">  </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Very service minded and friendly. <br />
    </span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Symbol;"><span style=""><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;"> </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Able to repair computers; finding out which part is broken and replacing it. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Able to help users with common computer related issues (knowledge of Maya, 3DS max, Photoshop etc is a plus). <o:p></o:p></span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Be methodical, thorough and organized. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Be a fan of video games and enjoy playing them. Having played many different types of games and on various platforms is a plus. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Have good analytical skills and an eye for detail.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
    <li><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="">Excellent spoken and written English. <o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="">Spanish and/or Catalan knowledge is considered a very big plus.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="">Previous testing experience is a plus. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="">Working knowledge of Linux or other non Windows platforms is a plus. <br />
Experience with web servers, versioning systems, scripting (VBA, Perl or other), general networking or Clavister products is also a plus. <o:p></o:p></span></p></span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="column_nav">
        <span class="column_nav_cat">Contact</span>
        <p>
          Please send your application through the online form below, or by regular mail to
          our physical adress. If you prefer to send your application by email click
          <a href="&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#105;&#116;&#106;&#111;&#98;&#115;&#64;&#103;&#114;&#105;&#110;&#46;&#115;&#101;">here</a>.</p>
      </div>
